#. iGxiF
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"bm_id3155805\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>data; user data</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>user data; input</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>personal data input</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>personal data; cursor position</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>user data; cursor position</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ມູນ; ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້; ການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນສ່ວນຕົວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ມູນສ່ວນຕົວ; ຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້; ຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີ</bookmark_value>"

#. iDNyF
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155805\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010100.xhp\">User Data</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010100.xhp\">ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້</link>"

#. Trz9C
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"par_id3156410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optuserpage/OptUserPage\">Use this tab page to enter or edit user data.</ahelp> Some of the data may have already been entered by the user or system administrator when installing $[officename]."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optuserpage/OptUserPage\">ໃຊ້ໜ້າແຖບນີ້ເພື່ອປ້ອນ ຫຼື ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້.</ahelp> ຂໍ້ມູນບາງຢ່າງອາດຈະຖືກປ້ອນໄວ້ແລ້ວໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ ຫຼື ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບເມື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງ $[officename]."

#. 54GEJ
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User data is used by templates and Wizards in $[officename]. For example, the \"First name\" and \"Last name\" data fields are used to automatically insert your name as the author of a new document. You can see this under <emph>File - Properties</emph>."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ແມ່ນຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໂດຍແມ່ແບບ ແລະ ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງ (Wizards) ໃນ $[officename]. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ \"ຊື່\" ແລະ \"ນາມສະກຸນ\" ແມ່ນໃຊ້ເພື່ອແຊກຊື່ຂອງທ່ານເປັນຜູ້ຂຽນເອກະສານໃໝ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນສິ່ງນີ້ໄດ້ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ</emph>."

#. jQejy
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153031\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some of the user data is included automatically in an internal dictionary so that it is recognized by the spellchecker. If typing errors are made, the program can use this data to suggest replacements. Note that changes to data take effect only after $[officename] is restarted."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ບາງຢ່າງຈະຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນພົດຈະນານຸກົມພາຍໃນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຕົວສະກົດຄຳຮັບຮູ້ໄດ້. ຖ້າມີການພິມຜິດ, ໂປຣແກຣມສາມາດໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ເພື່ອແນະນຳຄຳປ່ຽນແທນ. ໝາຍເຫດ: ການປ່ຽນແປງຂໍ້ມູນຈະມີຜົນຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ $[officename] ຖືກເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃໝ່ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. 9axWS
#: 01010100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153032\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User data is also used when commenting and in tracking changes mode, to identify comments/edits author; and to mark last edit position in document, so that when author opens the document later, it opens at the last edit position."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ຍັງຖືກນຳໃຊ້ເມື່ອມີການສະແດງຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ ແລະ ໃນໂໝດຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ ເພື່ອລະບຸຜູ້ຂຽນຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ/ການແກ້ໄຂ; ແລະ ເພື່ອໝາຍຕຳແໜ່ງການແກ້ໄຂຫຼ້າສຸດໃນເອກະສານ, ເພື່ອວ່າເມື່ອຜູ້ຂຽນເປີດເອກະສານໃນພາຍຫຼັງ, ມັນຈະເປີດຢູ່ຕຳແໜ່ງການແກ້ໄຂຫຼ້າສຸດ."

#. AhHXy
