"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optpathspage/OptPathsPage\">This section contains the default paths to important folders in $[officename]. These paths can be edited by the user.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optpathspage/OptPathsPage\">ສ່ວນນີ້ປະກອບດ້ວຍເສັ້ນທາງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໄປຫາໂຟນເດີທີ່ສຳຄັນໃນ $[officename]. ເສັ້ນທາງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້.</ahelp>"

