msgid "The paths refer to subdirectories in <literal>{install}</literal><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">\\</caseinline><defaultinline>/</defaultinline></switchinline><literal>share</literal>. These subdirectories are read-only and contain content shown to all users. The location of the <literal>{install}</literal> directory is determined when %PRODUCTNAME is installed."
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງອ້າງອີງເຖິງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີຍ່ອຍໃນ <literal>{install}</literal><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">\\</caseinline><defaultinline>/</defaultinline></switchinline><literal>share</literal>. ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີຍ່ອຍເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເປັນແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ ແລະ ປະກອບດ້ວຍເນື້ອຫາທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທຸກຄົນເຫັນ. ສະຖານທີ່ຂອງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ <literal>{install}</literal> ແມ່ນຖືກກຳນົດເມື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງ %PRODUCTNAME."

