"01010800.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149262\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Show preview of fonts"
msgstr "ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງຂອງຟອນ"

#. EbQfv
#: 01010800.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01010800.xhp\n"
"par_id3155415\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optviewpage/showfontpreview\">Displays the names of selectable fonts in the corresponding font, for example, fonts in the Font box on the <emph>Formatting</emph> bar.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optviewpage/showfontpreview\">ສະແດງຊື່ຂອງຟອນທີ່ສາມາດເລືອກໄດ້ໃນຮູບແບບຟອນນັ້ນໆ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຟອນໃນຊ່ອງຟອນເທິງແຖບ <emph>ການຈັດຮູບແບບ</emph>.</ahelp>"

#. bPXzY
#: 01010800.xhp
msgctxt ""
