msgstr "ເລືອກຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງແທັບໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ."

#. QiAXQ
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Accessibility"
msgstr "ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ"

#. NEsnD
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"bm_id3159411\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>disabled persons</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>text colors for better accessibility</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>animations; accessibility options</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Help tips; hiding</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>high contrast mode</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>accessibility; options</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>options; accessibility</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຜູ້ພິການ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ສີຂໍ້ຄວາມເພື່ອການເຂົ້າເຖິງທີ່ດີຂຶ້ນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ; ຕົວເລືອກການເຂົ້າເຖິງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄຳແນະນຳການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ; ການເຊື່ອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ໂໝດຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ; ຕົວເລືອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວເລືອກ; ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ</bookmark_value>"

#. E7FGE
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3159411\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01013000.xhp\">Accessibility</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01013000.xhp\">ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ</link>"

#. JpUGi
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149827\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Sets options that make %PRODUCTNAME programs more accessible for users with reduced sight, limited dexterity or other disabilities.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວເລືອກທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ໂປຣແກຣມ %PRODUCTNAME ເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນສຳລັບຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ມີບັນຫາທາງສາຍຕາ, ການເຄື່ອນໄຫວທີ່ຈຳກັດ ຫຼື ຄວາມພິການອື່ນໆ.</ahelp>"

#. qaFrR
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id851764671806995\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Animations"
msgstr "ພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ"

#. MfJvy
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id151764671655472\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>System</emph>: previews the animation of animated images according to system settings."
msgstr "<emph>ລະບົບ</emph>: ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງລະບົບ."

#. ksgFr
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id691764671661497\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Yes/No</emph>: enable or disable animations."
msgstr "<emph>ແມ່ນ/ບໍ່</emph>: ເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດໃຊ້ງານພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ."

#. ZyzDd
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147531\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allow animated images"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ"

#. fcgeF
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145069\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/animatedgraphics\">Previews animated graphics, such as GIF images, in %PRODUCTNAME.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/animatedgraphics\">ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງກຣາບຟິກເຄື່ອນໄຫວ ເຊັ່ນ ຮູບພາບ GIF ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME.</ahelp>"

#. BzB8J
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147264\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allow animated text"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດຂໍ້ຄວາມເຄື່ອນໄຫວ"

#. CEEXL
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149656\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/animatedtext\">Previews animated text, such as blinking and scrolling, in %PRODUCTNAME.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/animatedtext\">ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງຂໍ້ຄວາມເຄື່ອນໄຫວ ເຊັ່ນ ການກະພິບ ແລະ ການເລື່ອນ ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME.</ahelp>"

#. pZbGW
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id711764671914626\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allow other animations"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວອື່ນໆ"

#. B3CxA
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id121764672103857\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controls if certain other animations (for example 'marching ants' animation when copying a cell in Calc) are enabled."
msgstr "ຄວບຄຸມວ່າຈະໃຫ້ເປີດໃຊ້ພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວອື່ນໆ ຫຼື ບໍ່ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: ພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ 'ມົດຍ່າງ' ເມື່ອຄັດລອກເຊວໃນ Calc)."

#. EDRfa
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149809\n"
"help.text"
msgid "High contrast"
msgstr "ຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງ (High contrast)"

#. ADWvt
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153106\n"
"help.text"
msgid "High contrast is an operating system setting that changes the system color scheme to improve readability. You can decide how %PRODUCTNAME uses the high contrast settings of the operating system."
msgstr "ຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງ (High contrast) ແມ່ນການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງລະບົບປະຕິບັດການທີ່ປ່ຽນຊຸດສີຂອງລະບົບເພື່ອປັບປຸງການອ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດຕັດສິນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າຈະໃຫ້ %PRODUCTNAME ໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງຂອງລະບົບປະຕິບັດການແນວໃດ."

#. 3GueN
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3125863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cell borders and shadows are always shown in text color when high contrast mode is active. The cell background color is ignored then."
msgstr "ຂອບເຊວ ແລະ ເງົາຈະຖືກສະແດງເປັນສີຂໍ້ຄວາມສະເໝີເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ໂໝດຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງ. ສີພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງເຊວຈະຖືກລະເລີຍໃນກໍລະນີນັ້ນ."

#. nAE9N
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id421764672434711\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Automatic</emph>: uses high contrast according to system settings."
msgstr "<emph>ອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph>: ໃຊ້ຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງລະບົບ."

#. st6Jd
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id341764672439782\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Disable/Enable</emph>: overrides the high contrast system settings."
msgstr "<emph>ປິດ/ເປີດ</emph>: ຍົກເລີກການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງຂອງລະບົບ."

#. adddF
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154918\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use automatic font color for screen display"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ສີຟອນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບການສະແດງຜົນໜ້າຈໍ"

#. 258E8
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3146984\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/autofontcolor\">Displays fonts in %PRODUCTNAME using the system color settings. This option only affects the screen display.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/autofontcolor\">ສະແດງຟອນໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ໂດຍໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າສີຂອງລະບົບ. ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ມີຜົນສະເພາະກັບການສະແດງຜົນໜ້າຈໍເທົ່ານັ້ນ.</ahelp>"

#. ACMLB
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153091\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use system colors for page previews"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ສີຂອງລະບົບສຳລັບການສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງໜ້າ"

#. gdDWF
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3146923\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/systempagepreviewcolor\">Applies the high contrast settings of the operating system to page previews.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/systempagepreviewcolor\">ນຳໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງສີສູງຂອງລະບົບປະຕິບັດການກັບການສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງໜ້າ.</ahelp>"

#. fmTrF
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3166460\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Miscellaneous options"
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກອື່ນໆ"

#. dqDv8
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154047\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use text selection cursor in read-only text document"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ເຄີເຊີ (Cursor) ເລືອກຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນເອກະສານແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ"

#. h2CAX
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149164\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/textselinreadonly\">Displays cursor in read-only documents.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optaccessibilitypage/textselinreadonly\">ສະແດງເຄີເຊີໃນເອກະສານແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ.</ahelp>"

#. gfghv
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id611764672751039\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Accessibility Check Options"
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກການກວດສອບການເຂົ້າເຖິງ"

#. ossQB
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id341764673244852\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enable the accessibility checks for %PRODUCTNAME. These checks are performed when you select <menuitem>Tools - Accessibility Check</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ການກວດສອບການເຂົ້າເຖິງສຳລັບ %PRODUCTNAME. ການກວດສອບເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະດຳເນີນການເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກ <menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ການກວດສອບການເຂົ້າເຖິງ</menuitem>."

#. HuToc
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"hd_id361764673263739\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enable All"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ທັງໝົດ"

#. Sw7qx
#: 01013000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01013000.xhp\n"
"par_id421764673482109\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enables all available accessibility check options."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກການກວດສອບການເຂົ້າເຖິງທີ່ມີຢູ່ທັງໝົດ."

#. 3Terk
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Load/Save options"
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກການໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ"

#. GQv4p
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147291\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Load/Save options"
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກການໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ"

#. ajt3N
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3146957\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"laden\"><ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"visible\">Specifies general Load/Save settings. </ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"laden\"><ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"visible\">ກຳນົດການຕັ້ງຄ່າການໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກທົ່ວໄປ. </ahelp></variable>"

#. Ps5c6
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Proxy"
msgstr "ພຣັອກຊີ (Proxy)"

#. covY4
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>settings; proxies</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>proxy settings</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ; ພຣັອກຊີ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າພຣັອກຊີ</bookmark_value>"

#. xu6mb
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156414\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01020100.xhp\">Proxy</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01020100.xhp\">ພຣັອກຊີ (Proxy)</link>"

#. 25FcL
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145090\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#proxy\">Proxy servers</link> for accessing the Internet can be set up manually as needed."
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#proxy\">ເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີ (Proxy servers)</link> ສຳລັບການເຂົ້າເຖິງອິນເຕີເນັດສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າດ້ວຍຕົນເອງຕາມຄວາມຕ້ອງການ."

#. NBdSR
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ"

#. ZqA93
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines the settings for the <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#proxy\">proxy server</link>."
msgstr "ກຳນົດການຕັ້ງຄ່າສຳລັບ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#proxy\">ເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີ</link>."

#. DJ6pi
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Proxy server"
msgstr "ເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີ"

#. U7wuU
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3147275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/proxymode\">Specifies the type of proxy definition.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/proxymode\">ກຳນົດປະເພດຂອງການລະບຸພຣັອກຊີ.</ahelp>"

#. zb4ia
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147574\n"
"help.text"
msgid "None"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີ"

#. CTpxk
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Accesses the Internet without a proxy server. Allows you to set up a connection directly on your computer to an Internet provider that does not use a proxy."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເຖິງອິນເຕີເນັດໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີ. ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໂດຍກົງຈາກຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານໄປຍັງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການອິນເຕີເນັດທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ພຣັອກຊີ."

#. dpLKJ
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150984\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "ກຳນົດເອງ"

#. cR8GG
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3156155\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Lets you enter the proxy server manually. Specify the proxy servers in accordance with your Internet service. Ask your system administrator for the proxies and ports to enter."
msgstr "ໃຫ້ທ່ານປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ. ລະບຸເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີໃຫ້ສອດຄ່ອງກັບບໍລິການອິນເຕີເນັດຂອງທ່ານ. ສອບຖາມຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບກ່ຽວກັບພຣັອກຊີ ແລະ ພອດ (Ports) ທີ່ຈະປ້ອນ."

#. j2vBv
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Type server names without the protocol prefix. For example, type www.example.com, not http://www.example.com."
msgstr "ພິມຊື່ເຊີເວີໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃສ່ຄຳນຳໜ້າໂປຣໂຕຄໍ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ພິມ www.example.com, ບໍ່ແມ່ນ http://www.example.com."

#. HbPRw
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_idN10684\n"
"help.text"
msgid "System"
msgstr "ລະບົບ"

#. FASzj
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_idN10688\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On Windows or UNIX systems using GNOME or KDE, this option tells %PRODUCTNAME to use the system settings. You must restart %PRODUCTNAME to initiate this setting."
msgstr "ໃນລະບົບ Windows ຫຼື UNIX ທີ່ໃຊ້ GNOME ຫຼື KDE, ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຈະບອກໃຫ້ %PRODUCTNAME ໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງລະບົບ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ %PRODUCTNAME ໃໝ່ເພື່ອໃຫ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ມີຜົນ."

#. uyi5M
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148948\n"
"help.text"
msgid "HTTP proxy"
msgstr "HTTP ພຣັອກຊີ"

#. E7kmc
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154923\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/http\">Type the name of the proxy server for <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#http\">HTTP</link>.</ahelp> Type the port in the right-hand field."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/http\">ພິມຊື່ຂອງເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີສຳລັບ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#http\">HTTP</link>.</ahelp> ພິມໝາຍເລກພອດໃນຊ່ອງທາງດ້ານຂວາ."

#. DC73X
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id9971922\n"
"help.text"
msgid "HTTPS proxy"
msgstr "HTTPS ພຣັອກຊີ"

#. KRbfa
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id5319071\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Type the name of the proxy server for HTTPS. Type the port in the right-hand field.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ພິມຊື່ຂອງເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີສຳລັບ HTTPS. ພິມໝາຍເລກພອດໃນຊ່ອງທາງດ້ານຂວາ.</ahelp>"

#. 2XBfa
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3125863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "No proxy for"
msgstr "ບໍ່ໃຊ້ພຣັອກຊີສຳລັບ"

#. mnAQA
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151178\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/noproxy\">Specifies the names of the servers that do not require any proxy servers, separated by semicolons.</ahelp> These are servers addressed in your local network, and servers used for video and audio streaming, for example."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/noproxy\">ກຳນົດຊື່ຂອງເຊີເວີທີ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ພຣັອກຊີ, ແຍກກັນດ້ວຍໝາຍຈຸດຈ້ຳ (semicolons).</ahelp> ຕົວຢ່າງ: ເຊີເວີທີ່ຢູ່ໃນເຄືອຂ່າຍພາຍໃນຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ເຊີເວີທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບການສະຕຣີມມິງວິດີໂອ ແລະ ສຽງ."

#. DquNj
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also use placeholders for the names of hosts and domains. For example, type *.sun.com to address all the hosts in the sun.com domain without proxy."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ຕົວແທນ (placeholders) ສຳລັບຊື່ໂຮສຕ໌ (hosts) ແລະ ໂດເມນໄດ້. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ພິມ *.sun.com ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງໂຮສຕ໌ທັງໝົດໃນໂດເມນ sun.com ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ພຣັອກຊີ."

#. pgv7r
#: 01020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153666\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/httpsport\">Type the port for the corresponding proxy server.</ahelp> The maximum value of a port number is fixed at 65535."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optproxypage/httpsport\">ພິມໝາຍເລກພອດສຳລັບເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ.</ahelp> ຄ່າສູງສຸດຂອງໝາຍເລກພອດແມ່ນ 65535."

#. 7oGRX
#: 01020300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020300.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Email"
msgstr "ອີເມລ"

#. 8iAf5
#: 01020300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020300.xhp\n"
"par_idN1054D\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01020300.xhp\">Email</link>"
