#. EJCGw
#: 01030300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030300.xhp\n"
"par_idN1068B0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allows you to choose between different installed key store locations to use when signing ODF documents or exporting signed PDF. (Only on systems that use the Network Security Services NSS.)"
msgstr "ໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກລະຫວ່າງສະຖານທີ່ເກັບຄີ (key store) ທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ຕ່າງໆ ເພື່ອໃຊ້ໃນການເຊັນເອກະສານ ODF ຫຼື ການສົ່ງອອກ PDF ທີ່ເຊັນແລ້ວ. (ສະເພາະໃນລະບົບທີ່ໃຊ້ Network Security Services NSS ເທົ່ານັ້ນ.)"

#. ukDcL
#: 01030300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030300.xhp\n"
"par_idN1068E0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Certificate"
msgstr "ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ"

#. FRqVV
#: 01030300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01030300.xhp\n"
"par_idN106920\n"
"help.text"
