#. JHe6k
#: 01040200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01040200.xhp\n"
"par_id3153364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/viewoptionspage/smoothscroll\">Activates the smooth page scrolling function. </ahelp> The scrolling speed depends of the area and of the color depth display."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/viewoptionspage/smoothscroll\">ເປີດໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນການເລື່ອນໜ້າແບບລຽບນຽນ. </ahelp> ຄວາມໄວໃນການເລື່ອນຂຶ້ນກັບພື້ນທີ່ ແລະ ຄວາມເລິກຂອງສີໃນການສະແດງຜົນ."

