"par_id3153988\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/TpViewPage\">Defines which elements of the <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc main window are displayed. You can also show or hide highlighting of values in tables.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/TpViewPage\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງອົງປະກອບໃດແດ່ຂອງໜ້າຕ່າງຫຼັກຂອງ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງການເນັ້ນຄ່າໃນຕາຕະລາງໄດ້ນຳ.</ahelp>"

#. F2CEt
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id111715611366567\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - View</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ມຸມມອງ</menuitem>."

#. USQUC
