"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/comment_indicator.png\" id=\"img_id501718821081517\" width=\"159px\" height=\"96px\"><alt id=\"alt_id91718821081519\">Comment indicator</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/comment_indicator.png\" id=\"img_id501718821081517\" width=\"159px\" height=\"96px\"><alt id=\"alt_id91718821081519\">ຕົວບົ່ງບອກຄຳເຫັນ</alt></image>"

#. T4iFp
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150487\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:NoteVisible\">To display a comment permanently, select the <emph>Show comment</emph> command from the cell's context menu.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:NoteVisible\">ເພື່ອສະແດງຄຳເຫັນໄວ້ຕະຫຼອດເວລາ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ <emph>ສະແດງຄຳເຫັນ</emph> ຈາກເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງຫ້ອງນັ້ນ.</ahelp>"

#. Dk85Q
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3149667\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can type and edit comments with the <link href=\"text/shared/01/04050000.xhp\"><emph>Insert - Comment</emph></link> command. Comments that are permanently displayed can be edited by clicking the comment box. Click the Navigator and under the <emph>Comments</emph> entry you can view all comments in the current document. By double clicking a comment in Navigator, the cursor will jump to the corresponding cell containing the comment."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດພິມ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຄຳເຫັນໄດ້ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ <link href=\"text/shared/01/04050000.xhp\"><emph>ແຊກ - ຄຳເຫັນ</emph></link>. ຄຳເຫັນທີ່ສະແດງໄວ້ຕະຫຼອດເວລາສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ກ່ອງຄຳເຫັນ. ຄລິກທີ່ Navigator ແລະ ພາຍໃຕ້ຫົວຂໍ້ <emph>ຄຳເຫັນ</emph> ທ່ານຈະສາມາດເບິ່ງຄຳເຫັນທັງໝົດໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ. ໂດຍການດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ຄຳເຫັນໃນ Navigator, ເຄີເຊີຈະໂດດໄປຫາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງທີ່ມີຄຳເຫັນນັ້ນ."

#. T78Zm
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id261715605964558\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Comment authorship"
msgstr "ຜູ້ຂຽນຄຳເຫັນ"

#. RjWVM
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id111715605983990\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If this box is checked, the author of the comment and the date and time at which the comment was made will appear in the comment window, when you mouse over a comment."
msgstr "ຖ້າເລືອກຊ່ອງນີ້, ຊື່ຜູ້ຂຽນຄຳເຫັນ ລວມທັງວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາທີ່ຂຽນຄຳເຫັນຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຄຳເຫັນ ເມື່ອທ່ານເອົາເມົາສ໌ໄປວາງໄວ້ເທິງຄຳເຫັນ."

#. tYLiN
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id611716209450981\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The comment author name appears as it appears in the <emph>First Name</emph> and <emph>Last Name</emph> fields in the <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010100.xhp#name\"><emph>User Data</emph></link> dialog. If those fields are blank, the author name appears as \"Unknown Author\". Updating the user data only affects comments made after the update."
msgstr "ຊື່ຜູ້ຂຽນຄຳເຫັນຈະປາກົດຕາມທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊື່</emph> ແລະ <emph>ນາມສະກຸນ</emph> ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010100.xhp#name\"><emph>ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້</emph></link>. ຖ້າຊ່ອງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນວ່າງຢູ່, ຊື່ຜູ້ຂຽນຈະປາກົດເປັນ \"Unknown Author\". ການອັບເດດຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈະມີຜົນສະເພາະກັບຄຳເຫັນທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຫຼັງຈາກການອັບເດດເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. rRMZW
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id171694714728232\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Formula indicator and hint"
msgstr "ຕົວບົ່ງບອກສູດ ແລະ ຄຳແນະນຳ"

#. YE3Zg
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id971694714844904\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Draws a blue triangle in the bottom-left corner of a cell that contains a formula.  When pointing over the blue triangle, the formula is shown in a tool tip even if a different cell is selected."
msgstr "ສະແດງຮູບສາມຫຼ່ຽມສີຟ້າຢູ່ມຸມຊ້າຍລຸ່ມຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ມີສູດຢູ່. ເມື່ອເອົາເມົາສ໌ໄປຊີ້ໃສ່ສາມຫຼ່ຽມສີຟ້ານັ້ນ, ສູດຈະຖືກສະແດງໃນຮູບແບບ tool tip ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະເລືອກຫ້ອງອື່ນຢູ່ກໍຕາມ."

#. dDPB8
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id381718821990330\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/formula_indicator.png\" id=\"img_id631718821990332\" width=\"120px\" height=\"58px\"><alt id=\"alt_id141718821990334\">Formula indicator</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/formula_indicator.png\" id=\"img_id631718821990332\" width=\"120px\" height=\"58px\"><alt id=\"alt_id141718821990334\">ຕົວບົ່ງບອກສູດ</alt></image>"

#. qmC7Q
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150872\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Value highlighting"
msgstr "ການເນັ້ນຄ່າ"

#. 8aPEg
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154792\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/value\">Mark the <emph>Value highlighting</emph> box to show the cell contents in different colors, depending on type. Text cells are formatted in black, formulas in green, number cells in blue, and protected cells are shown with light grey background, no matter how their display is formatted.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/value\">ໝາຍເອົາຊ່ອງ <emph>ການເນັ້ນຄ່າ</emph> ເພື່ອສະແດງເນື້ອຫາໃນຫ້ອງເປັນສີຕ່າງໆ ຕາມປະເພດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນ. ຫ້ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະເປັນສີດຳ, ສູດຈະເປັນສີຂຽວ, ຫ້ອງຕົວເລກຈະເປັນສີຟ້າ, ແລະ ຫ້ອງທີ່ຖືກປ້ອງກັນຈະສະແດງດ້ວຍພື້ນຫຼັງສີເທົາອ່ອນ, ໂດຍບໍ່ສົນວ່າການສະແດງຜົນຂອງມັນຈະຖືກຈັດຮູບແບບໄວ້ແນວໃດ.</ahelp>"

#. qEmEC
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151319\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When this command is active, any colors assigned in the document will not be displayed until the function is deactivated."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ເຮັດວຽກ, ສີໃດໆ ກໍຕາມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນເອກະສານຈະບໍ່ຖືກສະແດງ ຈົນກວ່າຟັງຊັນນີ້ຈະຖືກປິດການໃຊ້ງານ."

#. qjxpC
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id441715869656096\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Column/Row highlighting"
msgstr "ການເນັ້ນຄໍລຳ/ແຖວ"

#. 95fif
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id311715869701090\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When this command is active, the column and row of a selected cell is highlighted. If multiple cells are selected, only the column and row of the first cell is highlighted."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ເຮັດວຽກ, ຄໍລຳ ແລະ ແຖວຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ຖືກເລືອກຈະຖືກເນັ້ນໃຫ້ເຫັນ. ຖ້າເລືອກຫຼາຍຫ້ອງ, ຈະມີພຽງຄໍລຳ ແລະ ແຖວຂອງຫ້ອງທຳອິດເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ຖືກເນັ້ນ."

#. PEjWg
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id381718822527122\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/row_col_highlight.png\" id=\"img_id251718822527124\" width=\"280px\" height=\"146px\"><alt id=\"alt_id571718822527126\">Column/Row highlighting</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/row_col_highlight.png\" id=\"img_id251718822527124\" width=\"280px\" height=\"146px\"><alt id=\"alt_id571718822527126\">ການເນັ້ນຄໍລຳ/ແຖວ</alt></image>"

#. hfcFM
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id301715869411090\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Highlight cell in edit mode"
msgstr "ເນັ້ນຫ້ອງໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ"

#. ZwybY
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id221715869527909\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When this command is active, the background of a cell is highlighted when it is in edit mode."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ເຮັດວຽກ, ພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງຫ້ອງຈະຖືກເນັ້ນໃຫ້ເຫັນເມື່ອມັນຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

#. FriUe
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id311718822104991\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/edit_highlight.png\" id=\"img_id661718822104993\" width=\"163px\" height=\"66px\"><alt id=\"alt_id941718822104996\">Highlight cell in edit mode</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/edit_highlight.png\" id=\"img_id661718822104993\" width=\"163px\" height=\"66px\"><alt id=\"alt_id941718822104996\">ເນັ້ນຫ້ອງໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ</alt></image>"

#. mKCDj
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3157846\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Anchor"
msgstr "ການຍຶດຕິດ (Anchor)"

#. AkAj6
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3147494\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/anchor\">Specifies whether the anchor icon is displayed when an inserted object, such as a graphic, is selected.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/anchor\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງໄອຄອນການຍຶດຕິດ (anchor) ຫຼື ບໍ່ ເມື່ອວັດຖຸທີ່ແຊກເຂົ້າມາ ເຊັ່ນ ຮູບພາບ ຖືກເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. 4GEe4
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id141718822193497\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/anchor.png\" id=\"img_id721718822193499\" width=\"308px\" height=\"255px\"><alt id=\"alt_id551718822193501\">Image anchor</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/anchor.png\" id=\"img_id721718822193499\" width=\"308px\" height=\"255px\"><alt id=\"alt_id551718822193501\">ການຍຶດຕິດຮູບພາບ</alt></image>"

#. eMNiE
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150327\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Show references in color"
msgstr "ສະແດງການອ້າງອີງເປັນສີ"

#. T24A7
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153766\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/rangefind\">Specifies that each reference is highlighted in color in the formula. The cell range is also enclosed by a colored border as soon as the cell containing the reference is selected for editing.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/rangefind\">ລະບຸວ່າການອ້າງອີງແຕ່ລະອັນຈະຖືກເນັ້ນດ້ວຍສີໃນສູດ. ຊ່ວງຂອງຫ້ອງ (cell range) ຈະຖືກອ້ອມຮອບດ້ວຍເສັ້ນຂອບທີ່ມີສີ ທັນທີທີ່ຫ້ອງທີ່ມີການອ້າງອີງນັ້ນຖືກເລືອກເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂ.</ahelp>"

#. nz5sA
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id531718822934064\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/refs_in_color.png\" id=\"img_id181718822934066\" width=\"326px\" height=\"156px\"><alt id=\"alt_id121718822934068\">References in color</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/refs_in_color.png\" id=\"img_id181718822934066\" width=\"326px\" height=\"156px\"><alt id=\"alt_id121718822934068\">ການອ້າງອີງເປັນສີ</alt></image>"

#. uGmMv
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153682\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Visual aids"
msgstr "ຕົວຊ່ວຍທາງສາຍຕາ"

#. wC3Lt
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153311\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies which lines are displayed."
msgstr "ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງເສັ້ນໃດແດ່."

#. Nfd2b
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147242\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Grid lines"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງ"

#. ZU82E
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/grid\" visibility=\"visible\">Specifies when grid lines will be displayed. Default is to display grid lines only on cells that do not have a background color. You can choose to also display grid lines on cells with background color, or to hide them.</ahelp> For printing, choose <emph>Format - Page Style - </emph><link href=\"text/scalc/01/05070500.xhp\"><emph>Sheet</emph></link> and mark the <emph>Grid</emph> check box."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/grid\" visibility=\"visible\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງເມື່ອໃດ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນສະແດງເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງສະເພາະຫ້ອງທີ່ບໍ່ມີສີພື້ນຫຼັງເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກໃຫ້ສະແດງເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງໃນຫ້ອງທີ່ມີສີພື້ນຫຼັງນຳ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງພວກມັນໄວ້ກໍໄດ້.</ahelp> ສຳລັບການພິມ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຮູບແບບໜ້າ - </emph><link href=\"text/scalc/01/05070500.xhp\"><emph>ແຜ່ນງານ</emph></link> ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຊ່ອງ <emph>ເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງ</emph>."

#. BFFBw
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id131715608178914\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pointer"
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້"

#. ucn54
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id471715608193873\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies whether %PRODUCTNAME Calc displays the pointer in the system default style, or the style which matches the icon theme."
msgstr "ລະບຸວ່າ %PRODUCTNAME Calc ຈະສະແດງຕົວຊີ້ໃນຮູບແບບເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງລະບົບ ຫຼື ຮູບແບບທີ່ກົງກັບຮູບແບບໄອຄອນ (icon theme)."

#. io6DW
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id221715609620456\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Themed"
msgstr "ຕາມຮູບແບບ (Themed)"

#. AwDnq
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id331715609634665\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shows the pointer as defined by the icon theme, typically as a fat cross."
msgstr "ສະແດງຕົວຊີ້ຕາມທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍຮູບແບບໄອຄອນ, ເຊິ່ງປົກກະຕິຈະເປັນຮູບກາກບາດໜາ."

#. LMvd3
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id351718822706632\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/cursor_themed.png\" id=\"img_id281718822706634\" width=\"86px\" height=\"55px\"><alt id=\"alt_id171718822706636\">Themed cursor</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/cursor_themed.png\" id=\"img_id281718822706634\" width=\"86px\" height=\"55px\"><alt id=\"alt_id171718822706636\">ຕົວຊີ້ຕາມຮູບແບບ</alt></image>"

#. hCRGM
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id1001715609641174\n"
"help.text"
msgid "System"
msgstr "ລະບົບ"

#. EhJuR
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id31715609645437\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shows the pointer as the system default, typically as an arrow."
msgstr "ສະແດງຕົວຊີ້ຕາມຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງລະບົບ, ເຊິ່ງປົກກະຕິຈະເປັນຮູບລູກສອນ."

#. 4n7Uj
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id951718822797834\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/cursor_system.png\" id=\"img_id681718822797836\" width=\"71px\" height=\"72px\"><alt id=\"alt_id41718822797838\">System cursor</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/cursor_system.png\" id=\"img_id681718822797836\" width=\"71px\" height=\"72px\"><alt id=\"alt_id41718822797838\">ຕົວຊີ້ຂອງລະບົບ</alt></image>"

#. y2GVB
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152349\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Page breaks"
msgstr "ການຂຶ້ນໜ້າໃໝ່"

#. svCrA
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151245\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/break\">Specifies whether to view the page breaks within a defined print area.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/break\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ເບິ່ງການຂຶ້ນໜ້າໃໝ່ພາຍໃນພື້ນທີ່ການພິມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ ຫຼື ບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. tZFL4
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Helplines While Moving"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຊ່ວຍໃນຂະນະທີ່ຍ້າຍ"

#. cFxtH
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148550\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/guideline\">Specifies whether to view guides when moving drawings, frames, graphics and other objects.</ahelp> These guides help you align objects."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/guideline\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງເສັ້ນນຳທາງເມື່ອຍ້າຍວັດຖຸແຕ້ມ, ກອບ, ຮູບພາບ ແລະ ວັດຖຸອື່ນໆ ຫຼື ບໍ່.</ahelp> ເສັ້ນນຳທາງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດວັດຖຸໃຫ້ຊື່ກັນໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. AL2Gp
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155444\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Objects"
msgstr "ວັດຖຸ"

#. gAcCG
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148405\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines whether to display or hide objects for up to three object groups."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງວັດຖຸສຳລັບກຸ່ມວັດຖຸສູງສຸດສາມກຸ່ມ."

#. ZyF26
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150043\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Objects/Images"
msgstr "ວັດຖຸ/ຮູບພາບ"

#. DMhEf
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3163549\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/objgrf\">Defines if objects and graphics are shown or hidden.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/objgrf\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງວັດຖຸ ແລະ ຮູບພາບ.</ahelp>"

#. GtMcZ
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151249\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Charts"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມ"

#. VfaGz
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3149106\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/diagram\">Defines if charts in your document are shown or hidden.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/diagram\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງແຜນພູມໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp>"

#. FfY8B
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154703\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drawing objects"
msgstr "ວັດຖຸແຕ້ມ"

#. BJFym
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3155959\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/draw\">Defines if drawing objects in your document are shown or hidden.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/draw\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງວັດຖຸແຕ້ມໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp>"

#. FRGCQ
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153920\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Window"
msgstr "ໜ້າຕ່າງ"

#. 7qgDf
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154661\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies whether some Help elements will or will not appear in the table."
msgstr "ລະບຸວ່າອົງປະກອບຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອບາງຢ່າງຈະປາກົດ ຫຼື ບໍ່ປາກົດໃນຕາຕະລາງ."

#. ykr7s
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149923\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Column/Row headers"
msgstr "ຫົວຄໍລຳ/ຫົວແຖວ"

#. BasRo
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3149816\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/rowcolheader\">Specifies whether to display row and column headers.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/rowcolheader\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງຫົວແຖວ ແລະ ຫົວຄໍລຳ ຫຼື ບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. d5GAX
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154205\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Horizontal scrollbar"
msgstr "ແຖບເລື່ອນແນວນອນ"

#. Z7vrm
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3155578\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/hscroll\">Specifies whether to display a horizontal scrollbar at the bottom of the document window.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/hscroll\">ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງແຖບເລື່ອນແນວນອນທີ່ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງໜ້າຕ່າງເອກະສານ ຫຼື ບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. UTVoE
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148422\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Vertical scrollbar"
msgstr "ແຖບເລື່ອນແນວຕັ້ງ"

#. Xx6aC
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3147128\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/vscroll\">Specifies whether to display a vertical scrollbar at the right of the document window.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/vscroll\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງແຖບເລື່ອນແນວຕັ້ງຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງປ່ອງຢ້ຽມເອກະສານຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. Aid3Q
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150826\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Sheet tabs"
msgstr "ແຖບຊີດ"

#. zEFP5
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/tblreg\">Specifies whether to display the sheet tabs at the bottom of the spreadsheet document.</ahelp> If this box is not checked, you will only be able to switch between the sheets through the <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/02110000.xhp\">Navigator</link></caseinline><defaultinline>Navigator</defaultinline></switchinline>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/tblreg\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງແຖບຊີດຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp> ຖ້າຫາກຫ້ອງນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໝາຍໄວ້, ທ່ານຈະສາມາດສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງຊີດຕ່າງໆໄດ້ຜ່ານ <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/02110000.xhp\">Navigator</link></caseinline><defaultinline>Navigator</defaultinline></switchinline> ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. ytaBT
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152584\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Outline symbols"
msgstr "ສັນຍະລັກໂຄງຮ່າງ"

#. AB5TU
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145135\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/outline\">If you have defined an <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/12080000.xhp\">outline</link></caseinline><defaultinline>outline</defaultinline></switchinline>, the <emph>Outline symbols</emph> option specifies whether to view the outline symbols at the border of the sheet.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/tpviewpage/outline\">ຖ້າຫາກທ່ານໄດ້ກຳນົດ <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/12080000.xhp\">ໂຄງຮ່າງ</link></caseinline><defaultinline>ໂຄງຮ່າງ</defaultinline></switchinline> ໄວ້, ຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ສັນຍະລັກໂຄງຮ່າງ</emph> ຈະກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງສັນຍະລັກໂຄງຮ່າງຢູ່ຂອບຂອງຊີດຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. DbySm
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id931715613945224\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Summary on search"
msgstr "ບົດສະຫຼຸບການຄົ້ນຫາ"

#. LgAVi
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id471715613958781\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If this box is checked, a Search Results window appears when you choose <menuitem>Find All</menuitem> in the <link href=\"text/shared/02/find_toolbar.xhp\"><menuitem>Find Bar</menuitem></link>. The Search Results box states the number of matching search results and lists:"
msgstr "ຖ້າຫາກໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງນີ້, ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກ <menuitem>ຄົ້ນຫາທັງໝົດ</menuitem> ໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/02/find_toolbar.xhp\"><menuitem>ແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ</menuitem></link>. ຫ້ອງຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຈະແຈ້ງຈຳນວນຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາທີ່ກົງກັນ ແລະ ລາຍການດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. VtT98
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id671715625666455\n"
"help.text"
msgid "the sheet where each result is located;"
msgstr "ຊີດທີ່ແຕ່ລະຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຕັ້ງຢູ່;"

#. DgERX
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id171715626207799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "the cell where each result is located; and"
msgstr "ເຊວທີ່ແຕ່ລະຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຕັ້ງຢູ່; ແລະ"

#. m8yZc
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id171715625670755\n"
"help.text"
msgid "the contents of the cell containing each result."
msgstr "ເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວທີ່ມີແຕ່ລະຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາ."

#. iQEKa
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id131715625842347\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Unchecking the <menuitem>Show this dialog</menuitem> box in the Search Results window disables this feature."
msgstr "ການຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຫ້ອງ <menuitem>ສະແດງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້</menuitem> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຈະເປັນການປິດການໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້."

#. RT3qR
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id0909200810585828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Zoom"
msgstr "ຊູມ"

#. ihBVU
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id0909200810585881\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Synchronize sheets"
msgstr "ເຮັດໃຫ້ຊີດສອດຄ່ອງກັນ"

#. Gq9P8
#: 01060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060100.xhp\n"
"par_id0909200810585870\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">If checked, all sheets are shown with the same zoom factor. If not checked, each sheet can have its own zoom factor.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຖ້າຫາກໝາຍເອົາ, ທຸກຊີດຈະຖືກສະແດງດ້ວຍອັດຕາການຊູມດຽວກັນ. ຖ້າບໍ່ໝາຍເອົາ, ແຕ່ລະຊີດສາມາດມີອັດຕາການຊູມເປັນຂອງຕົນເອງໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. bBVnj
#: 01060300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060300.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "General"
msgstr "ທົ່ວໄປ"

#. dNqQR
#: 01060300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060300.xhp\n"
"bm_id3151110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>metrics;in sheets</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>tab stops; setting in sheets</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>cells; cursor positions after input (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>edit mode; through Enter key (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>formatting; expanding (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>expanding formatting (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>references; expanding (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>column headers; highlighting (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>row headers; highlighting (Calc)</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການວັດແທກ;ໃນຊີດ</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ຈຸດຢຸດແທັບ; ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນຊີດ</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ເຊວ; ຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີຫຼັງຈາກການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ; ຜ່ານປຸ່ມ Enter (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ການຈັດຮູບແບບ; ການຂະຫຍາຍ (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ການຂະຫຍາຍການຈັດຮູບແບບ (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ການອ້າງອີງ; ການຂະຫຍາຍ (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ຫົວຖັນ; ການເນັ້ນ (Calc)</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ຫົວແຖວ; ການເນັ້ນ (Calc)</bookmark_value>"

