"01060400.xhp\n"
"par_id3150503\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/optsortlists/lists\">Displays all the available lists. These lists can be selected for editing.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/optsortlists/lists\">ສະແດງລາຍການທັງໝົດທີ່ມີຢູ່. ລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດເລືອກເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂໄດ້.</ahelp>"

