#. CXvon
#: 01060400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01060400.xhp\n"
"par_id3149669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/optsortlists/entries\">Displays the content of the currently selected list. This content can be edited.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/optsortlists/entries\">ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ. ເນື້ອໃນນີ້ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. 4Capq
