"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3147443\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/ruler\">Specifies whether to display the rulers at the top and to the left of the work area.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/ruler\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງບັນທັດຢູ່ທາງເທິງ ແລະ ທາງຊ້າຍຂອງພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp>"

#. XHYit
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Helplines While Moving"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຊ່ວຍວາງຂະນະທີ່ຍ້າຍ"

#. cobZu
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154147\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"helplines\"><variable id=\"verschieb\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Specifies whether to display guides when moving an object.</ahelp></variable></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"helplines\"><variable id=\"verschieb\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງເສັ້ນນຳທາງເມື່ອມີການຍ້າຍວັດຖຸຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp></variable></variable>"

#. fbFB6
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150488\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"vertext\"><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> creates dotted guides that extend beyond the box containing the selected object and which cover the entire work area, helping you position the object.</variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"vertext\"><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ຈະສ້າງເສັ້ນນຳທາງແບບຈຸດ ທີ່ຂະຫຍາຍອອກໄປນອກກອບຂອງວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກ ແລະ ກວມເອົາທົ່ວພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງວັດຖຸໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ.</variable>"

#. vir83
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You also can use this function through the <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"IMPRESS\"><link href=\"text/shared/02/01171400.xhp\">icon</link></caseinline><caseinline select=\"DRAW\"><link href=\"text/shared/02/01171400.xhp\">icon</link></caseinline><defaultinline>icon</defaultinline></switchinline> with the same name in the <emph>Options</emph> bar if a presentation or a drawing document is opened."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນນີ້ຜ່ານ <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"IMPRESS\"><link href=\"text/shared/02/01171400.xhp\">ໄອຄອນ</link></caseinline><caseinline select=\"DRAW\"><link href=\"text/shared/02/01171400.xhp\">ໄອຄອນ</link></caseinline><defaultinline>ໄອຄອນ</defaultinline></switchinline> ທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນໃນແຖບ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph> ຫາກມີເອກະສານການນຳສະເໜີ ຫຼື ເອກະສານການແຕ້ມເປີດຢູ່."

#. rNBhR
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155306\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All control points in Bézier editor"
msgstr "ຈຸດຄວບຄຸມທັງໝົດໃນຕົວແກ້ໄຂ Bézier"

#. NW5o8
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153877\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/handlesbezier\">Displays the control points of all Bézier points if you have previously selected a <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#bezierobject\">Bézier curve</link>. If the <emph>All control points in Bézier</emph> editor option is not marked, only the control points of the selected Bézier points will be visible.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/handlesbezier\">ສະແດງຈຸດຄວບຄຸມຂອງທຸກໆຈຸດ Bézier ຖ້າທ່ານໄດ້ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#bezierobject\">ເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ Bézier</link> ໄວ້ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ໝາຍເອົາຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ຈຸດຄວບຄຸມທັງໝົດໃນ Bézier</emph>, ຈະເຫັນສະເພາະຈຸດຄວບຄຸມຂອງຈຸດ Bézier ທີ່ຖືກເລືອກເທົ່ານັ້ນ.</ahelp>"

#. aDatu
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149418\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Contour of each individual object"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຂອບຂອງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸ"

#. TtRjv
#: 01070100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01070100.xhp\n"
"par_id3156284\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/moveoutline\"><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> displays the contour line of each individual object when moving this object.</ahelp> The <emph>Contour of each individual object </emph>option enables you to see if single objects conflict with other objects in the target position. If you do not mark the <emph>Contour of each individual object </emph>option, <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> only displays a square contour that includes all selected objects."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/simpress/ui/sdviewpage/moveoutline\"><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ສະແດງເສັ້ນຂອບຮູບຮ່າງຂອງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ ເມື່ອມີການຍ້າຍວັດຖຸນີ້.</ahelp> ຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ເສັ້ນຂອບຮູບຮ່າງຂອງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ</emph> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຫັນວ່າວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງໄປທັບຊ້ອນກັບວັດຖຸອື່ນໃນຕຳແໜ່ງເປົ້າໝາຍຫຼືບໍ່. ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ໝາຍເອົາຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ເສັ້ນຂອບຮູບຮ່າງຂອງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ</emph>, <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ຈະສະແດງພຽງແຕ່ເສັ້ນຂອບຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມທີ່ລວມເອົາທຸກວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

