#. NjJhB
#: 01090100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01090100.xhp\n"
"par_id301756326562748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Reduces or enlarges the size of the formula code by a specified scale factor."
msgstr "ຫຼຸດ ຫຼື ຂະຫຍາຍຂະໜາດຂອງລະຫັດສູດຕາມຕົວຄູນປັບຂະໜາດທີ່ກໍານົດ."

#. E52AX
