#. PeqhX
#: 01110100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01110100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optchartcolorspage/colors\">Displays all the colors available for the data series.</ahelp> Select a data series to change its color. Select the desired color from the adjacent color table."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optchartcolorspage/colors\">ສະແດງສີທັງໝົດທີ່ມີສຳລັບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp> ເລືອກຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນເພື່ອປ່ຽນສີຂອງມັນ. ເລືອກສີທີ່ຕ້ອງການຈາກຕາຕະລາງສີທີ່ຢູ່ຂ້າງໆ."

#. wHA9i
