#. 7NTkC
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id3159399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"codetext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Loads and saves the Basic code from a Microsoft document as a special $[officename] Basic module with the document. The disabled Microsoft Basic code is visible in the $[officename] Basic IDE between <emph>Sub</emph> and <emph>End Sub</emph>.</ahelp> You can edit the code. When saving the document in $[officename] format, the Basic code is saved as well. When saving in another format, the Basic code from the $[officename] Basic IDE is not saved. </variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"codetext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ໂຫຼດ ແລະ ບັນທຶກລະຫັດ Basic ຈາກເອກະສານ Microsoft ໃຫ້ເປັນໂມດູນ $[officename] Basic ພິເສດພ້ອມກັບເອກະສານ. ລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ທີ່ຖືກປິດການໃຊ້ງານຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນໃນ $[officename] Basic IDE ລະຫວ່າງ <emph>Sub</emph> ແລະ <emph>End Sub</emph>.</ahelp> ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂລະຫັດໄດ້. ເມື່ອບັນທຶກເອກະສານໃນຮູບແບບ $[officename], ລະຫັດ Basic ຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໄປນຳ. ແຕ່ຫາກບັນທຶກໃນຮູບແບບອື່ນ, ລະຫັດ Basic ຈາກ $[officename] Basic IDE ຈະບໍ່ຖືກບັນທຶກ. </variable>"

#. r8Sve
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"hd_id0523200811475727\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Executable code"
msgstr "ລະຫັດທີ່ສາມາດເຮັດວຽກໄດ້"

#. b4EWB
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id0523200811475733\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">The VBA (Visual Basic for Applications) code will be loaded ready to be executed. If this checkbox is not checked, the VBA code will be commented out so it can be inspected, but will not run.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ລະຫັດ VBA (Visual Basic for Applications) ຈະຖືກໂຫຼດມາໃນສະພາບທີ່ພ້ອມເຮັດວຽກ. ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ໝາຍເລືອກໃນຊ່ອງນີ້, ລະຫັດ VBA ຈະຖືກໃສ່ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເຫັນ (comment out) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ກວດສອບໄດ້ເທົ່ານັ້ນ ແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດລັນໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. 6SjW7
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id05172017121531273\n"
"help.text"
msgid "After loading the VBA code, %PRODUCTNAME inserts the statement <item type=\"literal\">Option VBASupport 1</item> in every Basic module to enable a limited support for VBA statements, functions and objects. See <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03103350.xhp\">Option VBASupport Statement</link> for more information."
msgstr "ຫຼັງຈາກໂຫຼດລະຫັດ VBA, %PRODUCTNAME ຈະແຊກຄຳສັ່ງ <item type=\"literal\">Option VBASupport 1</item> ລົງໃນທຸກໆໂມດູນ Basic ເພື່ອເປີດການຮອງຮັບຄຳສັ່ງ, ຟັງຊັນ ແລະ ວັດຖຸ VBA ແບບຈຳກັດ. ເບິ່ງ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03103350.xhp\">Option VBASupport Statement</link> ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. rC252
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153824\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Save original Basic code"
msgstr "ບັນທຶກລະຫັດ Basic ຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#. 4vufq
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150084\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Specifies that the original Microsoft Basic code contained in the document is held in a special internal memory for as long as the document remains loaded in $[officename]. When saving the document in Microsoft format the Microsoft Basic is saved again with the code in an unchanged form.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ກໍານົດໃຫ້ລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ຕົ້ນສະບັບທີ່ຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳພາຍໃນພິເສດ ຕາບໃດທີ່ເອກະສານຍັງຖືກໂຫຼດຢູ່ໃນ $[officename]. ເມື່ອບັນທຶກເອກະສານໃນຮູບແບບ Microsoft, ລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ຈະຖືກບັນທຶກຄືນໃໝ່ໃນຮູບແບບທີ່ບໍ່ມີການປ່ຽນແປງ.</ahelp>"

#. ExbdF
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When saving in another format than Microsoft Format, the Microsoft Basic Code is not saved. For example, if the document contains Microsoft Basic Code and you save it in $[officename] format, you will be warned that the Microsoft Basic Code will not be saved."
msgstr "ເມື່ອບັນທຶກໃນຮູບແບບອື່ນທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນຮູບແບບຂອງ Microsoft, ລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ຈະບໍ່ຖືກບັນທຶກ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຫາກເອກະສານມີລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ແລະ ທ່ານບັນທຶກມັນໃນຮູບແບບ $[officename], ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບການເຕືອນວ່າລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ຈະບໍ່ຖືກບັນທຶກ."

#. YCZCR
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151246\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Save original Basic code</emph> checkbox takes precedence over the <emph>Load Basic code</emph> check box. If both boxes are marked and you edit the disabled Basic Code in the $[officename] Basic IDE, the original Microsoft Basic code will be saved when saving in the Microsoft format. A message appears to inform you of this."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງໝາຍ <emph>ບັນທຶກລະຫັດ Basic ຕົ້ນສະບັບ</emph> ຈະມີສິດສູງກວ່າຊ່ອງໝາຍ <emph>ໂຫຼດລະຫັດ Basic</emph>. ຫາກໝາຍທັງສອງຊ່ອງ ແລະ ທ່ານແກ້ໄຂລະຫັດ Basic ທີ່ຖືກປິດການໃຊ້ງານໃນ $[officename] Basic IDE, ລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic ຕົ້ນສະບັບຈະຖືກບັນທຶກເມື່ອບັນທຶກໃນຮູບແບບ Microsoft. ຈະມີຂໍ້ຄວາມປະກົດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ທ່ານຊາບກ່ຽວກັບເລື່ອງນີ້."

#. PmM96
#: 01130100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01130100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148946\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To remove any possible Microsoft Basic macro viruses from the Microsoft document, unmark the <emph>Save Original Basic Code </emph>check box and save the document in Microsoft format. The document will be saved without the Microsoft Basic code."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບໄວຣັສມັກໂຄ (macro viruses) ທີ່ອາດມີຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານ Microsoft, ໃຫ້ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍເລືອກໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ບັນທຶກລະຫັດ Basic ຕົ້ນສະບັບ</emph> ແລ້ວບັນທຶກເອກະສານໃນຮູບແບບ Microsoft. ເອກະສານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໂດຍບໍ່ມີລະຫັດ Microsoft Basic."

