#. D5qrK
#: 01150200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01150200.xhp\n"
"par_id3152996\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines the search options for Japanese."
msgstr "ກໍານົດຕົວເລືອກການຄົ້ນຫາສຳລັບພາສາຍີ່ປຸ່ນ."

#. EizFd
