"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/connpooloptions/timeout\">Defines the time in seconds after which a pooled connection is freed.</ahelp> The time can be anywhere between 30 and 600 seconds."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/connpooloptions/timeout\">ກໍານົດເວລາເປັນວິນາທີ ຫຼັງຈາກນັ້ນການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ລວມກຸ່ມໄວ້ຈະຖືກປົດປ່ອຍໃຫ້ວ່າງ.</ahelp> ເວລາສາມາດຕັ້ງໄດ້ລະຫວ່າງ 30 ຫາ 600 ວິນາທີ."

