"BasicIDE.xhp\n"
"par_id2507201509433451\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optbasicidepage/autoclose_quotes\">Automatically close open quotes.</ahelp> %PRODUCTNAME Basic IDE will add a closing quote each time you type an opening quote. Handy for inserting strings in the Basic code."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optbasicidepage/autoclose_quotes\">ປິດເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າທີ່ເປີດໄວ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ.</ahelp> %PRODUCTNAME Basic IDE ຈະເພີ່ມເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າຕົວປິດໃຫ້ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານພິມຕົວເປີດ. ສະດວກຫຼາຍສຳລັບການແຊກຂໍ້ຄວາມ (string) ໃນລະຫັດ Basic."

