#. eMvPG
#: expertconfig.xhp
msgctxt ""
"expertconfig.xhp\n"
"par_id0709201509091312\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"literal\">string</item>: Alphanumeric values;"
msgstr "<item type=\"literal\">string</item>: ຄ່າຕົວອັກສອນ ແລະ ຕົວເລກ;"

#. CWMmX
