msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/optionen/java.xhp\">ຂັ້ນສູງ</link>"

#. EvCZY
#: java.xhp
msgctxt ""
"java.xhp\n"
"par_idN10568\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies the support options for Java applications in %PRODUCTNAME, including which Java Runtime Environment (JRE) to use. It also specifies whether to use experimental (unstable) features such as macro recording and access expert configuration."
msgstr "ກໍານົດຕົວເລືອກການຮອງຮັບສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ Java ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME, ລວມທັງການເລືອກໃຊ້ Java Runtime Environment (JRE). ນອກຈາກນີ້ຍັງກໍານົດວ່າຈະໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດທົດລອງ (ທີ່ບໍ່ສະຖຽນ) ເຊັ່ນ ການບັນທຶກມັກໂຄ ແລະ ການເຂົ້າເຖິງການຕັ້ງຄ່າແບບຊ່ຽວຊານຫຼືບໍ່."

#. 85s2b
#: java.xhp
msgctxt ""
"java.xhp\n"
"par_idN1056B\n"
"help.text"
