"par_idN10635\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optadvancedpage/add\">Add a path to the root folder of a JRE on your computer.</ahelp> The path is set in the following dialog."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/optadvancedpage/add\">ເພີ່ມເສັ້ນທາງໄປຫາໂຟນເດີຫຼັກ (root folder) ຂອງ JRE ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp> ເສັ້ນທາງຈະຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນໜ້າຈໍຖັດໄປ."

